    <item>
      <title>莫迪的挫折之年让印度在危险的 2025 年变得脆弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/modi-s-year-of-setbacks-leaves-india-vulnerable-in-perilous-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年初，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 正乘着国际热潮，期待着一场看似走形式、却被他称作千年传承的竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/modi-s-year-of-setbacks-leaves-india-vulnerable-in-perilous-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
